data.description: You are going to fall in love with this gorgeous home in Strongsville! Step up to the striking black double doors that lead into the beautiful open foyer with high ceilings and a grand staircase! Off of the foyer is the spacious living room! The living room features large picture windows overlooking the front yard allowing for tons of natural light! With plush carpeting, you are lead into the open dining area with plenty of room for seating making it the perfect space to gather and entertaining! Continue through to the incredibly spacious eat-in kitchen featuring tons of counterspace, cabinets that wrap around the room and a lovely double sink! Off of the kitchen you will find an additional room featuring a gorgeous brick fireplace with mantel, exposed beams across the ceiling and sliding glass doors that lead out to the large backyard! The first-floor half bathroom has wrap around counters and gorgeous flooring! You will also find an additional room that can be used as an office, bedroom or extra living space! Upstairs you will find 4 incredibly spacious bedrooms! The master bedroom has tons of closet space and is complete with a private full bathroom featuring double vanity sinks and a standing shower! The 2nd full bathroom also offers a double sink and a shower/tub combination! The convenient 2nd floor laundry room features a sink, counterspace and plenty of cabinets for storage! Outside you will find an incredibly spacious backyard with a deck that leads off the back of the home! There is cental air and an attached 3-car garage! With easy access to highways this is near food, shopping and tons of public amenities! This won't last long! Schedule a showing to see it for yourself!
